-- Silgan Interested in Buying Turkey’s Ontas Oner, Sabah Says
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-05-29T07:08:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-29/silgan-interested-in-buying-turkey-s-ontas-oner-sabah-says.html
Silgan Holdings Inc. (SLGN) , the Stamford,
Conneticut-based producer of packaging products, is interested
in buying Turkey’s Ontas Oner,  Sabah  reported, without saying
how it got the information.  Silgan is looking to buy all of the Izmir-based company
from owner Erhan Oner, chief executive officer of  Tekfen Holding
AS (TKFEN) , Sabah said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  